text: Karagay () is a rural locality (a village) in Ilkineyevsky Selsoviet, Kuyurgazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 46 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 20 km from Yermolayevo, 3 km from Ilkineyevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kuyurgazinsky District
title: Karagay, Kuyurgazinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
